‚öôÔ∏è Data Overview

The STAR*D dataset includes:

Demographic information (age, gender, education, marital status);

Clinical evaluations (HAM-D, QIDS, and other depression severity scales);

Treatment information across multiple phases;

Psychometric and cognitive test scores;

Family and substance use history.

This diversity of variables allows both cross-sectional and longitudinal analyses, supporting advanced predictive modeling in mental health.
